flowchart TD
    Q[SQL 谓词、表达式、类型、Collation] --> P[Planner 规范化与选择率估算]
    P --> M{操作符是否属于索引 Opclass/Opfamily?}
    M -- 否 --> S[Seq Scan 或其他索引]
    M -- 是 --> AM{Access Method}

    AM --> GIN[GIN: 提取键 -> Entry Tree]
    GIN --> PL[Posting List / Posting Tree]
    GIN --> PD[Pending List]

    AM --> GIST[GiST: Consistent / Union]
    GIST --> GP[Penalty / PickSplit]
    GIST --> GK[KNN Distance]

    AM --> SP[SP-GiST: Prefix + Nodes]
    SP --> ST[Quad/KD/Radix 分区]

    AM --> BR[BRIN: Block Range Summary]
    BR --> BS[Minmax / Multi / Bloom / Inclusion]

    AM --> H[Hash: 32-bit Hash -> Bucket]

    PL --> C[候选 TID 或距离有序 TID]
    GP --> C
    GK --> C
    ST --> C
    BS --> C
    H --> C
    PD --> C

    C --> BM[Bitmap Index/Heap Scan 或 Index Scan]
    BM --> MVCC[Heap Tuple + Snapshot 可见性检查]
    MVCC --> R{需要 Recheck?}
    R -- 是 --> E[重新执行原始操作符]
    R -- 否 --> O[返回结果]
    E --> O

    PD --> CL[Vacuum/Autoanalyze/阈值触发清理]
    CL --> GIN
